      <p id="u835-4">The Zimnat Group,rebranded to highlight its association with the <span id="u835-2">Sanlam Group</span> in March 2017. Sanlam Emerging Markets (SEM), a subsidiary of Sanlam Limited in 2015 acquired a 40% shareholding in the Zimnat Group. Sanlam is a dominant financial services and insurance holding company, listed on the Johannesburg Stock Exchange. Sanlam has been in the insurance and life assurance business since 1918.</p>
